---
title: Salmon, Feta & Courgette Filo Galette with Orange Salad & Almonds
description: A summery festive season is very special, and deserves to be celebrated in style! Introducing our salmon, feta & courgette galette - wrapped in crispy, golden layers of filo pastry and filled with deliciously creamy feta and tender salmon, it's like a gift for your taste buds.
